To request commercial or educational use, contact the project owner at: [thomas@tsmithcode.ai]


Great question — here's a **clear, side-by-side comparison** of the two licenses:

---

### ✅ [Creative Commons BY-NC-ND 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/)  
**(Attribution–NonCommercial–NoDerivatives)**  
| Category                | Details |
|------------------------|---------|
| **Ownership Retained** | ✅ Yes – You keep full rights |
| **Attribution Required** | ✅ Yes – Must credit you |
| **Commercial Use**     | ❌ Not allowed without permission |
| **Educational Use**    | ❌ Not allowed without permission |
| **Modifications**      | ❌ No one can remix, adapt, or extend it |
| **Main Use Case**      | Ideal for showcasing a portfolio, demo, or internal tool where you want full control over reuse |

---
